     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZD18SHPV2DosesVS</b></p><a name=\"IMMZD18SHPV2DosesVS\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZD18SHPV2DosesVS\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 5 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SHPV2DosesVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Child's|20birth|20when|20client's|20biological|20sex|20is|20female-34\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Child.39sbirthwhenclient.39sbiologicalsexisfemale-34\">Child's birth when client's biological sex is female-34</a></td><td>Child's birth when client's biological sex is female</td><td><div><p>Child's birth AND \"Sex\" = \"Female\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SHPV2DosesVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-First|20HPV|20dose|20from|20the|20primary|20series|20was|20administered-112\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-FirstHPVdosefromtheprimaryserieswasadministered-112\">First HPV dose from the primary series was administered-112</a></td><td>First HPV dose from the primary series was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"HPV vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 1</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SHPV2DosesVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Second|20HPV|20dose|20from|20the|20primary|20series|20was|20administered-112\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-SecondHPVdosefromtheprimaryserieswasadministered-112\">Second HPV dose from the primary series was administered-112</a></td><td>Second HPV dose from the primary series was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"HPV vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 2</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SHPV2DosesVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Second|20HPV|20dose|20from|20the|20primary|20series|20was|20administered|20and|20client's|20HIV|20status|20is|20positive|20or|20client|20is|20immunocompromised-178\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-SecondHPVdosefromtheprimaryserieswasadministeredandclient.39sHIVstatusispositiveorclientisimmunocompromised-178\">Second HPV dose from the primary series was administered and client's HIV status is positive or client is immunocompromised-178</a></td><td>Second HPV dose from the primary series was administered and client's HIV status is positive or client is immunocompromised</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"HPV vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 2 AND (\"HIV status\" = \"HIV-positive\" OR \"Immunocompromised\" = TRUE)</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SHPV2DosesVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Third|20HPV|20dose|20from|20the|20primary|20series|20was|20administered-112\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-ThirdHPVdosefromtheprimaryserieswasadministered-112\">Third HPV dose from the primary series was administered-112</a></td><td>Third HPV dose from the primary series was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"HPV vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 3</p>\